<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Essence Partners — Em breve</title>
<meta name="description" content="Essence Partners — controladoria e consultoria empresarial. Em breve.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;500;600&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --navy-900:#081826;
    --navy-800:#0C2135;
    --gold:#C9A227;
    --gold-light:#E4C46A;
    --ivory:#F3EFE6;
    --muted:#8FA1B3;
  }
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
  html,body{height:100%;}
  body{
    background:radial-gradient(120% 120% at 50% -10%, var(--navy-800) 0%, var(--navy-900) 60%);
    color:var(--ivory);
    font-family:'Jost',sans-serif;
    font-weight:300;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    min-height:100vh;
  }
  main{
    flex:1;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    text-align:center;
    padding:2rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .eyebrow{
    font-size:.78rem;
    letter-spacing:.42em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--muted);
    animation:rise .9s ease both;
  }
  h1{
    font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
    font-weight:500;
    font-size:clamp(2.6rem,8vw,5.2rem);
    letter-spacing:.14em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    margin:1.4rem 0 0;
    line-height:1.05;
    animation:rise .9s .15s ease both;
  }
  h1 .amp{color:var(--gold-light);}
  .rule{
    width:72px;
    height:1px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--gold),transparent);
    margin:2rem auto;
    animation:grow 1.1s .35s ease both;
  }
  .soon{
    font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
    font-style:italic;
    font-size:clamp(1.25rem,3vw,1.7rem);
    color:var(--gold-light);
    letter-spacing:.06em;
    animation:rise .9s .5s ease both;
  }
  .sub{
    max-width:34rem;
    margin-top:1.1rem;
    font-size:.98rem;
    line-height:1.7;
    color:var(--muted);
    animation:rise .9s .65s ease both;
  }
  footer{
    padding:1.6rem;
    text-align:center;
    font-size:.72rem;
    letter-spacing:.28em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--muted);
  }
  @keyframes rise{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px);}to{opacity:1;transform:none;}}
  @keyframes grow{from{opacity:0;transform:scaleX(0);}to{opacity:1;transform:scaleX(1);}}
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
    .eyebrow,h1,.rule,.soon,.sub{animation:none;}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<main>
  <p class="eyebrow">Controladoria <span class="amp" style="color:var(--gold-light);">·</span> Consultoria Empresarial</p>
  <h1>Essence<br>Partners</h1>
  <div class="rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <p class="soon">Em breve</p>
  <p class="sub">Estamos preparando um novo espaço para apoiar a gestão e a tomada de decisão da sua empresa.</p>
</main>
<footer>© 2026 Essence Partners</footer>
</body>
</html>
